Hello Edwin,

Thank you for getting back to us. 

Does the IP that you are using is the one from the newly machine that is hosted on our end? 

Can you please login to the UI and from the System Configuration -> Client Software, download a new installation package and check if the situation persist? 

Also, regarding the devices, does the Device Rights are set to DENY for all devices ? 

Can you please check if, there is any devices added as allow or on an allowlist?

Looking forward for your response. 

Best regards,
